"content": "<h2>The mining of copper</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:9\">DEU 8:7–8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:2-Job28:10\">JOB 28:2–28:10</a></p>\n<h2>The smelting of copper</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:20-Ezek22:21\">EZK 22:20–22:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:18\">EZK 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:11\">EZK 24:11</a></p>\n<h2>Coins made of copper</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:9\">MAT 10:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:42\">MRK 12:41–12:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:2\">LUK 21:1–21:2</a> <em>Coins of various denominations were made of copper in late OT and in NT times.</em></p>",
